      <em>Questions to Consider:</em>
    </p>
    <p>
      <ul xml:id="m79900-fs-idm374078736">
        <li>
          <p>What makes a person safety conscious?</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>How can you improve your personal safety?</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
